@startuml
title Figure 18. Assistive AI CV Builder Activity Diagram
start
:Candidate selects\n"Tailor CV by Job";
:Enter experience data\nand target JD;
:Click AI optimization button;
:Frontend sends request\nto NestJS backend;
:Backend builds prompt\nand sends to Gemini API;
:Gemini analyzes context\nand returns structured output;

if (AI response valid?) then (Yes)
  :Backend returns clean data;
  :Frontend renders updated CV preview;
  if (User clicks Export PDF?) then (Yes)
    :html2canvas captures DOM layout;
    :jsPDF converts canvas to flat PDF;
    :Download CV PDF;
    stop
  else (No)
    :Keep preview on screen;
    stop
  endif
else (No)
  :Notify AI generation failure\nand allow retry;
  stop
endif
@enduml
